WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:01.235 --> 00:00:02.169
<i>Previously</i>
<i>on</i> Will Trent...

2
00:00:02.302 --> 00:00:03.805
Will Trent.

3
00:00:03.938 --> 00:00:05.640
Ava.

4
00:00:05.773 --> 00:00:11.078
It's my number. in case
you didn't have it or need
it or whatever.

5
00:00:16.149 --> 00:00:17.986
I'm going to
New York for a few weeks.

6
00:00:18.118 --> 00:00:21.421
- I'll text you when I get back.
- Maybe we can do it again.

7
00:00:23.257 --> 00:00:24.826
Not everything
has to be so serious.

8
00:00:25.259 --> 00:00:27.695
You know. I agree.
Not everything has
to be so serious.

9
00:00:27.829 --> 00:00:31.599
Someone told me that
recently and they-- she--
they have a point.

10
00:00:31.733 --> 00:00:33.835
Was it Ava? Was Ava
the "they/she/they"?

11
00:00:33.968 --> 00:00:36.871
By the way. I knew you
slept with her. I just know
how to mind my business.

12
00:00:37.005 --> 00:00:38.338
Eduardo. read text.

13
00:00:38.472 --> 00:00:41.108
<i>Text from Ava.</i>
<i>"Hey. sexy. send me a selfie."</i>

14
00:00:41.241 --> 00:00:42.442
One second.

15
00:00:42.877 --> 00:00:45.178
Oh. Will. she is not talking
about that kind of selfie.

16
00:00:45.312 --> 00:00:47.615
Oh. Oh. my. Really?

17
00:00:48.983 --> 00:00:50.552
I'll respond to her later.

18
00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:58.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
